title: Episode 224: Lip Service Live Tour Atlanta (Feat. Jhonni Blaze, Tokyo Jetz, Trouble, and YFN Lucci)
itunes:title: Episode 224: Lip Service Live Tour Atlanta (Feat. Jhonni Blaze, Tokyo Jetz, Trouble, and YFN Lucci)
description:
Jhonni Blaze, Tokyo Jetz, Trouble, and YFN Lucci joins the ladies of Lip Service for their pit stop in Atlanta. Tokyo Jetz opens up about motherhood, sex while pregnant, and other guys shooting their shot while she's pregnant. As you would expect, things get reckless when both Trouble and YFN Lucci join the ladies on stage together. They cover a range of topics including apologizing to their ex's, insecurities, cucumbers, and much more. Enjoy!
